          ],
          "FACILITY": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "facility": [
                  "VDG"
                ],
                "institute": "3AULAUA"
              },
              "free_text": [
                " 3 MeV Van de Graaff accelerator at",
                "Lucas heights."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "INC-SOURCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "incident_source": [
                  "P-LI7"
                ],
                "reaction": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                "     A proton energy 15 to 19 keV above",
                "threshold,(neutron energies of 10 to 80 keV).",
                "16keV thick lithium target."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Natural cadmium target (1119.7g, 15*15*0.61 cm3)."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TOF"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " For determination of neutron energies. Path=20cm.",
                "The neutron energy was also measured by the shift."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "GELI"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "  A Ge(Li) detector, ORTEC 40 cm3 coaxial, was",
                "used to measure neutron energy dependent yields of",
                "primary gamma-rays in Cd-111(n,g) and Cd-113(n,g)."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "MOXR"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " a Moxon-Rae detector was used to monitor the",
                "total capture gamma-rays to obtain the incident neutron",
                "flux."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "MONITOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Absolute normalisation of the partial cross-section was",
                "achieved using the ground state transition from the 35k",
                "resonance in aluminum. Assuming that the ground state",
                "transition intensity is 66 photons per 100 capture, a",
                "partial width of gamma(gamma C)=1.6+-0.2eV is obtained."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "CORRECTION": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
